## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/sparsesetvalfunctor">SparseSetValFunctor</a> - Helper class for selecting <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/sparsesetvaltraits">SparseSetValTraits</a>.

The generic implementation handles ValueT classes which either provide getSparseSetIndex() or specialize <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/sparsesetvaltraits">SparseSetValTraits&lt;&gt;</a>.
